text: Up the Chastity Belt is a 1971 British comedy movie directed by Bob Kellett and starring Frankie Howerd, Graham Crowden, Bill Fraser, Anna Quayle, Eartha Kitt, Roy Hudd, Godfrey Winn, Anne Aston, Iain Cuthbertson, Christopher Timothy, Long John Baldry, Frank Thornton, Patricia Quinn. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1971 comedy movies Category:British comedy movies Category:Movies based on TV series
title: Up the Chastity Belt
